# GitHub Linguist language stats tuning
# 目标：让仓库语言统计更准确地体现 Tauri(Rust) 后端，而不是被前端/构建产物“压住”。
#
# 说明：
# - linguist-generated: 生成物/构建产物，不计入语言统计
# - linguist-vendored: vendored/依赖/可忽略源码，不计入语言统计（但仍在仓库中）
# - linguist-detectable: 强制某目录可被统计（通常不需要，仅作为保险）

# --- Build artifacts (exclude) ---
dist/** linguist-generated=true
src-tauri/target/** linguist-generated=true
node_modules/** linguist-generated=true

# --- Frontend (exclude from language stats so Rust becomes dominant) ---
src/** linguist-vendored=true
index.html linguist-vendored=true
vite.config.js linguist-vendored=true

# --- JSON (exclude from language stats) ---
*.json linguist-vendored=true
*.lock linguist-vendored=true

# --- Rust (ensure detectable) ---
src-tauri/** linguist-detectable=true

